{"tid":196812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那，北泡，美帝局勢咁多版本，係唔係玩緊情報戰？","createTime":"2017-04-11T14:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T16:02:26.000Z","uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7026a40977b6f7a46f2e67ed2ae02286cdfb732","tid":196812,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:08:08.000Z","msg":"1. 美帝叫支那說服金仔逃亡<br />\n<br />\n2. 美帝聯合支那打北泡<br />\n<br />\n3. 美帝比機會金仔放棄核武就唔再攪佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實個目的係等金仔自亂陣腳？<br />\n<br />\n試探金仔中？<br />\n<br />\n因為確定北泡有核武<br />\n<br />\n所以驚狗急跳牆一鑊熟<br />\n<br />\n要慢慢拆彈？<br />\n<br />\n老老實實<br />\n<br />\n就算金仔射唔出核彈<br />\n<br />\n本土引爆都夠全地球有排受<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n討論下"},{"pid":"f566d10db129eac7abd89e6336dbb6eb0c49b996","tid":196812,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:09:40.000Z","msg":"15號 夠膽咪核試囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fe7c7787a15fc0cfcacb5606596105bdf294a7","tid":196812,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>15號 夠膽咪核試囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實最大隱憂<br />\n<br />\n係全地球無人摸得清金仔個底<br />\n<br />\n對住呢d可以用核武又未知底線既人究竟點handle?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b179bf1bd65b9bf8d58eea2e8577c2be8145f64","tid":196812,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a21eaee08081b0a34fedaf2277cc6d4cc89c124","tid":196812,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301b440ee1eb39d4f7a6f3e8ce65a3b0ddca64f